title: 4K - The Killer Shrews (1959) They must eat 3 times their weight each day... OR STARVE!

sources.title: 4K - The Killer Shrews (1959) They must eat 3 times their weight each day... OR STARVE!
sources.description:
Captain Thorne Sherman (James Best) lands his ship on an isolated island to make a delivery, only to find that mad doctor Marlowe Craigis (Baruch Lumet) is experimenting on shrews in an attempt to shrink them. The opposite happens, and the shrews become enormous and hungry for human flesh, leaving everyone on the island in peril, including the doctor's pretty daughter, Ann (Ingrid Goude) and her unappealing fiancé, Jerry (Ken Curtis). Then, Thorne tries to organize an escape plan.

Alternative title: The Night of the Eldritch Beasts (1959)
